contentText:
Travis Kelce gave now-fiancée Taylor Swift a brilliant cut diamond ring when he proposed in August, but when it came time to reveal which of the gifts he&#8217;d given the superstar since they began their romance is her favorite, it wasn&#8217;t the bling that he mentioned.

